  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct intended for lumbar spinal fusion in adult patients. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level for Class II device submission support. Intended use is limited to static compression-bending loading per ASTM F1717; dynamic, torsional, and in vivo loading scenarios are explicitly out of scope.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-fea-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-static-compression-bending",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
