    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted at Medium assurance level. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted on the basis of regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 single-condition testing and the explicitly restricted scope of the intended use claim. The assessment team, regulatory affairs, and quality assurance have reviewed and endorsed this determination.",
